Dear Students,


You are invited to this week's talk in the "Leadership Lecture Series"
featuring alumni. The speaker is Dr. Santanu Paul ( BTCS, 1990), CEO and
MD, TalentSprint Private Limited, and the talk is on Friday, Sep 23, 2016
in IC & SR auditorium @ 5 pm.


NOTE: THERE WILL BE APPR. 30 LECTURES ARRANGED DURING THE 201617 ACADEMIC
YEAR. STUDENTS WHO ATTEND AT LEAST 80% OF THE LECTURES WILL BE GIVEN
